text: Filip Dumić (born October 8, 1990) is a Serbian professional basketball player who plays for Radnički Kragujevac of the Basketball League of Serbia. ==Professional career== On August 17, 2013, he signed with Borac Čačak. On January 22, 2018, Dumić signed with Romanian basketball club Timba Timișoara.
